title: 04/04/22 DPS Hour 1 - Final Four, Anthony Davis
itunes:title: 04/04/22 DPS Hour 1 - Final Four, Anthony Davis
description:
In hour 1 of the Dan Patrick Show, the guys recap the historic Final Four match up between Duke & UNC. The final game for Coach K! Also the guys speak on Anthony Davis return to the Lakers and his feelings about how the teams is being received.
